<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>MealMap - Home</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/Donor/donatehome.css">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="assets/logo.jpg" />
</head>
<body>
  <div class="app">
    <nav class="navbar">
      <div class="nav-logo"><img src="assets/logo.jpg"  alt="Foodkart logo">MealMap</div>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="#" class="active">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="donatefood">Donate Food</a></li>
        <li><a href="donorhistory">Mydonatios</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="hero-section">
      <div class="hero-overlay">
        <h1>Share Food, Spread Hope</h1>
        <p>Donate surplus food to fight hunger and build stronger communities.</p>
        <a href="donatefood" class="cta-button">Start Donating Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Why Donation is Important -->
    <div class="why-donate-section">
      <h2>Why Food Donation Matters</h2>
      <div class="why-donate-cards">
        <div class="why-donate-card">
          <img src="assets/donor/D1.jpg" alt="Reduce Waste Icon">
          <h3>Reduce Food Waste</h3>
          <p>Every year, tons of edible food are discarded. Your donations keep food out of landfills.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-donate-card">
          <img src="assets/donor/D2.jpg" alt="End Hunger Icon">
          <h3>End Hunger</h3>
          <p>Provide meals to families and individuals facing food insecurity in your area.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-donate-card">
          <img src="assets/donor/D3.jpg" alt="Build Community Icon">
          <h3>Build Community</h3>
          <p>Connect with local charities and neighbors through the power of sharing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- About MealMap -->
    <div class="about-section">
      <h2>About MealMap</h2>
      <p>MealMap is a platform dedicated to reducing food waste and fighting hunger. Our mission is to make it easy for individuals and businesses to donate surplus food to those in need. By connecting donors with local charities, we ensure that every meal counts.</p>
      <p>Join us to make a difference, one donation at a time!</p>
    </div>

    <!-- How Donation Works -->
    <div class="donation-info-section">
      <h2>How Donation Works</h2>
      <div class="donation-steps">
        <div class="step">
          <h3>1. List Your Donation</h3>
          <p>Upload an image, specify food type, quantity, and pickup details.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <h3>2. Get Matched</h3>
          <p>We connect you with nearby charities or volunteers to collect your donation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <h3>3. Track Progress</h3>
          <p>Follow your donation’s journey from pickup to delivery in the History section.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial Slider -->
    <div class="slider-section">
      <h2>What Our Users Say</h2>
      <div class="slider">
        <div class="slide">
          <img src="assets/donor/SLIDE1.jpg" alt="Sarah Donating" class="slide-image">
          <p>"Donating through MealMap is so easy! I love knowing my extra food helps others."</p>
          <h4>– Sarah, Local Donor</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <img src="assets/donor/SLIDE2.jpg" alt="Hope Charity" class="slide-image">
          <p>"MealMap connected us with donors to feed hundreds in our community."</p>
          <h4>– Hope Charity</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <img src="assets/donor/SLIDE3.jpg" alt="John Restaurant" class="slide-image">
          <p>"I feel great reducing waste and supporting my neighbors with MealMap."</p>
          <h4>– John, Restaurant Owner</h4>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQs -->
    <div class="faq-section">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <input type="checkbox" id="faq1" class="faq-toggle">
        <label for="faq1" class="faq-question">What types of food can I donate?</label>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>You can donate both perishable (e.g., fresh fruits, cooked meals) and non-perishable (e.g., canned goods, grains) food, as long as it’s safe and edible.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <input type="checkbox" id="faq2" class="faq-toggle">
        <label for="faq2" class="faq-question">How do I know my donation is safe?</label>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>We verify all donations through a process that ensures food safety. You’ll track the status (Pending, Accepted, Picked, Verified) in the History section.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <input type="checkbox" id="faq3" class="faq-toggle">
        <label for="faq3" class="faq-question">Who picks up my donation?</label>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Local charities or volunteers coordinated by MealMap will collect your donation at the specified time and location.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <input type="checkbox" id="faq4" class="faq-toggle">
        <label for="faq4" class="faq-question">Is there a minimum donation amount?</label>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>No minimum! Every bit helps, whether it’s a single meal or a large batch.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact Us -->
    <div class="contact-section">
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <div class="contact-content">
        <div class="contact-form">
          <h3>Send Us a Message</h3>
          <form>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="name">Name</label>
              <input type="text" id="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email">Email</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="message">Message</label>
              <textarea id="message" placeholder="Your Message" rows="5" required></textarea>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="submit-button">Send Message</button>
          </form>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-info">
          <h3>Get in Touch</h3>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> support@MealMap.org</p>
          <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +1 (555) 123-4567</p>
          <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Community Lane, Share City</p>
          <p>We're here to help with any questions about donating or using MealMap!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>